### ==============================================
### Kong Gateway API Testing
### ==============================================
### Direct User Service: http://localhost:8080
### Kong Proxy: http://localhost:8000
### Kong Admin API: http://localhost:8001
### Konga Dashboard: http://localhost:1337
### ==============================================
###
### DECLARATIVE CONFIG (recommended):
### Sync kong.yml to Kong using deck:
### docker run --rm --network kong-network -v $(pwd)/kong:/kong kong/deck:latest gateway sync /kong/kong.yml --kong-addr http://kong-gateway:8001
###
### ==============================================

@kong_proxy = http://localhost:8000
@kong_admin = http://localhost:8001
@direct_service = http://localhost:8080

### ==============================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### ==============================================

### Health check via Kong Proxy
GET {{kong_proxy}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check direct to service
GET {{direct_service}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Kong Admin API status
GET {{kong_admin}}/status
Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### USER SERVICE ENDPOINTS (via Kong Proxy)
### ==============================================

### Get all users
GET {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new user
POST {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

###

### Get user by ID (replace with actual ID)
@user_id = 6ed9d6e6-59c6-485d-9cf9-c4dc434c47da

GET {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update user
PUT {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete user
DELETE {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Services Management
### ==============================================

### List all services
GET {{kong_admin}}/services
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new service
POST {{kong_admin}}/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "user-service",
  "url": "http://user-service:8080"
}

###

### Get specific service
GET {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service
Accept: application/json

###

### Update service
PATCH {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "retries": 3,
  "connect_timeout": 30000
}

###

### Delete service
# DELETE {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service
# Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Routes Management
### ==============================================

### List all routes
GET {{kong_admin}}/routes
Accept: application/json

###

### Create route for user-service
POST {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service/routes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "user-service-route",
  "paths": ["/api/v1/users", "/health"],
  "strip_path": false
}

###

### Get specific route
GET {{kong_admin}}/routes/user-service-route
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete route
# DELETE {{kong_admin}}/routes/user-service-route
# Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Plugins Management
### ==============================================

### List all plugins
GET {{kong_admin}}/plugins
Accept: application/json

###

### Enable rate-limiting plugin for user-service
POST {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service/plugins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "rate-limiting",
  "config": {
    "minute": 100,
    "policy": "local"
  }
}

###

### Enable request-transformer plugin
POST {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service/plugins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "request-transformer",
  "config": {
    "add": {
      "headers": ["X-Gateway: Kong"]
    }
  }
}

###

### Enable cors plugin
POST {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service/plugins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "cors",
  "config": {
    "origins": ["*"],
    "methods": ["GET", "POST", "PUT", "DELETE", "OPTIONS"],
    "headers": ["Accept", "Authorization", "Content-Type"],
    "credentials": true,
    "max_age": 3600
  }
}

###

### Enable basic-auth plugin
POST {{kong_admin}}/services/user-service/plugins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "basic-auth",
  "config": {
    "hide_credentials": true
  }
}

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Consumers Management
### ==============================================

### List all consumers
GET {{kong_admin}}/consumers
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a consumer
POST {{kong_admin}}/consumers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "api-user",
  "custom_id": "user-001"
}

###

### Add basic-auth credentials to consumer
POST {{kong_admin}}/consumers/api-user/basic-auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "api-user",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Test request with basic auth (after enabling basic-auth plugin)
GET {{kong_proxy}}/api/v1/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YXBpLXVzZXI6c2VjcmV0MTIz

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Upstreams & Targets (Load Balancing)
### ==============================================

### Create upstream for load balancing
POST {{kong_admin}}/upstreams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "user-service-upstream",
  "algorithm": "round-robin",
  "healthchecks": {
    "active": {
      "http_path": "/health",
      "healthy": {
        "interval": 5,
        "successes": 2
      },
      "unhealthy": {
        "interval": 5,
        "http_failures": 3
      }
    }
  }
}

###

### Add target to upstream
POST {{kong_admin}}/upstreams/user-service-upstream/targets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "user-service:8080",
  "weight": 100
}

###

### List upstream targets
GET {{kong_admin}}/upstreams/user-service-upstream/targets
Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Certificates (SSL/TLS)
### ==============================================

### List all certificates
GET {{kong_admin}}/certificates
Accept: application/json

###

### ==============================================
### KONG ADMIN API - Info & Debug
### ==============================================

### Get Kong node information
GET {{kong_admin}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Kong configuration
GET {{kong_admin}}/config
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all enabled plugins
GET {{kong_admin}}/plugins/enabled
Accept: application/json

###
